					</div>
					<h2>Radiation & Laser safety</h2>
 <h4>Procedures, guidelines, and other resources to support radiation users on campus, help ensure safety and make certain that radiation exposures are reduced to levels that are As Low As Reasonably Achievable (ALARA).</h4>
		</div>
	</div>
	
				
		</div>
									<div class="row">
		
    							
								
						
							    
			
				
		
	<div class="widget col-xs-12 col-md-8">
		<div class="widget-bucket clearfix">
			
			<h3>Guidelines</h3>
            <p>For UCI Medical Center radiation safety matters, contact Barbara Hamrick at (714) 456-5607, <a href="mailto:bhamrick@uci.edu">bhamrick@uci.edu</a>, or via campus mail: Bldg 27 Rte 107.</p>
            <h3>Radiation Safety</h3>
